title: Chapter I - Franchise and Certain Business Taxes
content:
Chapter I - Franchise and Certain Business Taxes

State Regulations

Subchapter A - Business Corporation Franchise Tax (Part 1 to 11)

Subchapter B - Franchise Tax On Banking Corporations (Part 16 to 30)

Subchapter C - Franchise Taxes On Insurance Corporations (Part 31 to 34)

Subchapter D - Corporate Tax Procedure And Administration (Part 35 to 39)

Subchapter E - Franchise Tax On Transportation And Transmission Corporations (Part 40 to 41)

Subchapter F - Tax On The Furnishing Of Utility Services (Part 44 to 49)

Subchapter G - Stock Transfer Tax (Part 50 to 56)

Subchapter H - Alcoholic Beverage Tax (Part 60 to 68)

Subchapter I - Cigarette Tax, Cigarette Marketing Standards And Tobacco Products Tax (Article 1 to 3)

Subchapter J - Taxes On Admissions To Race Meetings And On Pari-mutuel Wagering (Part 95 to 99)

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
